<db:para>Elements in the demo can be controlled using the mouse in the following ways:</db:para>
<db:itemizedlist>
<db:listitem>
<db:para>Dragging the mouse while pressing the left mouse button rotates the box in the center.</db:para>
</db:listitem>
<db:listitem>
<db:para>Dragging the mouse while pressing the right mouse button rotates the satellite boxes.</db:para>
</db:listitem>
<db:listitem>
<db:para>Scrolling the mouse wheel zooms in and out of the scene.</db:para>
</db:listitem>
</db:itemizedlist>
<db:para>The options pane can be used to fine-tune various parameters in the demo, including colors and pixel shaders.</db:para>
